# Project Safety Checkpoint

- Run `powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File tools/check-local.ps1` after every build or foundation change.
- Do not commit or push automatically; show changed files and summary first.
- Do not change the Git remote unless explicitly requested.
- Do not add page-load `CREATE TABLE`, `ALTER TABLE`, or schema repair code.
- Do not connect to OpenCart or use old OpenCart extension code.
- Keep the architecture channel-neutral for supplier operations, sales channels, manual/offline orders, payable/return workflows, and future multi-business expansion.
